      <ownedComment xmi:id="_qOVYHAWTEfGAS7nvoHpUTg">
        <body>objectTag: product
Trigger: view product
Basic Flow:  The system retrieves the selected product details, The system displays the product information (e.g., name, price, description), The system displays related options (e.g., add to cart, view recommendations).
Alternative flow: Customer selects “Add to Shopping Cart”
.</body>
      </ownedComment>
